{"tid":1880476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廁紙潮濕天氣易發霉養菌","createTime":"2020-02-15T00:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T00:34:57.000Z","uid":4574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"828d3b15604147326d5b3660d9af29f367a0a4bc","tid":1880476,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T00:34:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200214/60597336?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200214%2F60597336%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=323fb1df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200214%2F60597336%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=33f8c3f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200214/60597336?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】囤積廁紙有保障？何栢良警告潮濕天氣易發霉養菌 籲勿「損人不利己」<br />\n<br />\n早前有謠言流傳廁紙將缺貨，引發大批市民搶購，無論卷裝、盒裝紙巾還是廚房用的抹手紙，即使貨源充足，依然供不應求，超市廁紙貨架長期空空如也，即使政府多番澄清廁紙沒有缺貨問題，依然有大批人搶購囤積。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良提醒市民，香港2、3月天氣潮濕，不宜囤積廁紙，否則反會滋生細菌，強調儲備足夠使用量已夠。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良解釋，無論是廁紙還是盒裝紙巾，均未經過無菌處理，就算放在紙盒或膠袋中，紙張仍會吸水，易滋生細菌發霉，市民用來抹眼或如廁後使用，有機會影響影響健康。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8hFANm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8hFANm.jpg&h=73e79808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"142243c6debd542954a2efb125b26ba56fcf9ed8","tid":1880476,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T00:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}